N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4058.3 - Exemption from penalties in claiming race

State Regulations

When winners of claiming races are exempted from
penalties, the exemption shall apply only to the winner of a race in which some
of the horses are entered as "not to be claimed" if the winner of such a race
was entered for a claiming price. Notes
